<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>あおぞら司法書士事務所｜愛知県の会社設立・不動産登記の相談所</title>
<meta name="description" content="愛知県の司法書士事務所。会社設立・不動産登記のご相談はお気軽に。初めての方にも分かりやすく、丁寧にご説明します。">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@500;600;700;800&family=Zen+Maru+Gothic:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --cream: #FBF4EA;
    --cream-deep: #F5EBDA;
    --paper: #FFFCF6;
    --apricot: #F2A65A;
    --apricot-deep: #E08A3C;
    --seal: #C8633A;
    --ink: #5B4636;
    --ink-soft: #8A7561;
    --moss: #8FA888;
    --line: #E8D9C2;
    --shadow: 0 18px 40px -22px rgba(91,70,54,0.35);
  }

  *{box-sizing:border-box; margin:0; padding:0;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    font-family:'Zen Maru Gothic','Hiragino Maru Gothic ProN','Hiragino Sans',sans-serif;
    color:var(--ink);
    background:var(--cream);
    line-height:1.9;
    letter-spacing:0.02em;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  img{max-width:100%; display:block;}
  a{color:inherit; text-decoration:none;}
  ul{list-style:none;}

  h1,h2,h3,.serif{
    font-family:'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-weight:700;
    letter-spacing:0.06em;
  }

  .wrap{
    max-width:1080px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:0 28px;
  }

  /* ===== 紙のテクスチャ風背景 ===== */
  body{
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 8% 12%, rgba(242,166,90,0.10), transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 92% 4%, rgba(143,168,136,0.10), transparent 35%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 80%, rgba(242,166,90,0.07), transparent 45%);
  }

  /* ===== ヘッダー ===== */
  header{
    position:sticky;
    top:0;
    z-index:100;
    background:rgba(251,244,234,0.92);
    backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .header-inner{
    max-width:1080px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:18px 28px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
  }
  .logo{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:10px;
    font-family:'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size:19px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:var(--seal);
  }
  .logo-mark{
    width:38px; height:38px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:linear-gradient(155deg, var(--apricot), var(--seal));
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    color:#fff; font-size:16px; font-weight:700;
    flex-shrink:0;
  }
  nav{display:flex; gap:32px; align-items:center;}
  nav a{
    font-size:14.5px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:var(--ink);
    position:relative;
    padding:4px 0;
  }
  nav a::after{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    left:0; bottom:-2px;
    width:0; height:2px;
    background:var(--apricot);
    border-radius:2px;
    transition:width 0.25s ease;
  }
  nav a:hover::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-cta{
    background:var(--seal);
    color:#fff !important;
    padding:11px 22px;
    border-radius:999px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{background:var(--apricot-deep);}
  .menu-toggle{display:none; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; padding:6px;}
  .menu-toggle span{display:block; width:24px; height:2px; background:var(--ink); margin:5px 0; border-radius:2px;}

  /* ===== ヒーロー ===== */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    padding:84px 0 70px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero-inner{
    max-width:1080px;
    margin:0 auto;
    padding:0 28px;
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap:48px;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:8px;
    background:var(--paper);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    padding:8px 18px;
    border-radius:999px;
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:var(--seal);
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow .dot{width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--moss);}
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(32px, 4.4vw, 50px);
    line-height:1.5;
    color:var(--ink);
    margin-bottom:8px;
  }
  .hero h1 .accent{
    color:var(--seal);
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .hero h1 .underline{
    display:block;
    width:min(260px, 65%);
    height:auto;
    margin:-8px 0 0;
  }
  .hero-sub{
    margin-top:22px;
    font-size:16.5px;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
    line-height:2;
  }
  .hero-sub strong{color:var(--ink); font-weight:700;}
  .hero-ctas{
    margin-top:34px;
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:14px;
  }
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:8px;
    padding:16px 30px;
    border-radius:999px;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:15px;
    transition:transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--seal);
    color:#fff;
    box-shadow:0 14px 30px -10px rgba(200,99,58,0.55);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px); background:var(--apricot-deep);}
  .btn-secondary{
    background:var(--paper);
    color:var(--ink);
    border:1.5px solid var(--line);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px); border-color:var(--apricot);}
  .hero-note{
    margin-top:18px;
    font-size:13px;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:8px;
  }

  /* ヒーローのイラスト：朱印（はんこ）モチーフ + 会話の吹き出し */
  .hero-art{
    position:relative;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
  }
  .hero-art svg{width:100%; max-width:420px; height:auto;}

  /* ===== セクション共通 ===== */
  section{padding:96px 0;}
  .section-head{
    text-align:center;
    max-width:640px;
    margin:0 auto 56px;
  }
  .section-eyebrow{
    font-size:13px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:var(--moss);
    letter-spacing:0.18em;
    margin-bottom:14px;
    display:block;
  }
  .section-head h2{
    font-size:clamp(26px, 3.4vw, 36px);
    color:var(--ink);
    line-height:1.6;
  }
  .section-head p{
    margin-top:18px;
    color:var(--ink-soft);
    font-size:15.5px;
  }

  /* ===== 共感パート（悩み） ===== */
  .worry{
    background:var(--paper);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .worry-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap:20px;
  }
  .worry-card{
    background:var(--cream);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:24px;
    padding:30px 28px;
    display:flex;
    gap:18px;
    align-items:flex-start;
  }
  .worry-card .icon{
    flex-shrink:0;
    width:52px; height:52px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:#fff;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .worry-card p{font-size:15.5px; color:var(--ink); font-weight:500; line-height:1.8;}
  .worry-foot{
    text-align:center;
    margin-top:40px;
    font-size:16px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:var(--seal);
  }

  /* ===== 解決提示 ===== */
  .solution{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap:56px;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .solution-art svg{width:100%; height:auto;}
  .solution-text h2{
    font-size:clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
    line-height:1.7;
    margin-bottom:24px;
  }
  .solution-text p{color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:15.5px; margin-bottom:16px;}
  .solution-callout{
    margin-top:28px;
    background:var(--cream-deep);
    border-left:4px solid var(--apricot);
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:22px 26px;
    font-size:15px;
    font-weight:500;
    color:var(--ink);
  }

  /* ===== 強み ===== */
  .strengths{background:var(--paper); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .strengths-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap:28px;
  }
  .strength-card{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px 26px;
    background:var(--cream);
    border-radius:28px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    transition:transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }
  .strength-card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px); box-shadow:var(--shadow);}
  .strength-num{
    width:64px; height:64px;
    margin:0 auto 22px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:linear-gradient(155deg, var(--apricot), var(--seal));
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  }
  .strength-card h3{font-size:18px; margin-bottom:14px; color:var(--ink);}
  .strength-card p{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-soft);}

  /* ===== サービス ===== */
  .services-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap:28px;
  }
  .service-card{
    background:var(--paper);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:28px;
    overflow:hidden;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .service-top{
    padding:34px 34px 0;
  }
  .service-tag{
    display:inline-block;
    font-size:12.5px;
    font-weight:700;
    background:var(--cream-deep);
    color:var(--seal);
    padding:6px 14px;
    border-radius:999px;
    margin-bottom:16px;
  }
  .service-card h3{font-size:21px; margin-bottom:12px;}
  .service-card p{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom:24px;}
  .service-art{padding:0 24px;}
  .service-art svg{width:100%; height:auto;}
  .service-link{
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;
    padding:18px 34px;
    background:var(--cream-deep);
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:14.5px;
    color:var(--seal);
  }

  /* ===== 流れ ===== */
  .flow{background:var(--paper); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .flow-list{
    position:relative;
    max-width:760px;
    margin:0 auto;
  }
  .flow-list::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    left:31px;
    top:14px;
    bottom:14px;
    width:2px;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--apricot) 0, var(--apricot) 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 13px);
  }
  .flow-item{
    position:relative;
    display:flex;
    gap:26px;
    padding:0 0 44px 0;
  }
  .flow-item:last-child{padding-bottom:0;}
  .flow-num{
    flex-shrink:0;
    width:64px; height:64px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--cream);
    border:2px solid var(--apricot);
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Shippori Mincho', serif;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:var(--seal);
    z-index:1;
  }
  .flow-item.is-last .flow-num{background:var(--seal); border-color:var(--seal); color:#fff;}
  .flow-body{padding-top:10px;}
  .flow-body h3{font-size:17.5px; margin-bottom:8px; color:var(--ink);}
  .flow-body p{font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-soft);}

  /* ===== 代表メッセージ ===== */
  .rep{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:0.85fr 1.15fr;
    gap:56px;
    align-items:center;
  }
  .rep-photo{
    position:relative;
  }
  .rep-photo svg{width:100%; height:auto;}
  .rep-name-badge{
    position:absolute;
    bottom:-18px; right:-12px;
    background:var(--paper);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:16px 22px;
    box-shadow:var(--shadow);
  }
  .rep-name-badge .role{font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-soft); font-weight:700;}
  .rep-name-badge .name{font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); margin-top:2px;}
  .rep-text .quote-mark{font-size:48px; color:var(--apricot); font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif; line-height:1; margin-bottom:6px;}
  .rep-text p{font-size:15.5px; color:var(--ink); margin-bottom:18px;}
  .rep-text p.lead{font-size:17px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.9;}
  .rep-sign{margin-top:28px; font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif; font-size:15px; color:var(--ink-soft);}

  /* ===== FAQ ===== */
  .faq{background:var(--paper); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .faq-list{max-width:760px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;}
  .faq-item{
    background:var(--cream);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:26px 30px;
  }
  .faq-q{display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:flex-start; font-weight:700; font-size:15.5px; color:var(--ink); margin-bottom:12px;}
  .faq-q .qa-mark{
    flex-shrink:0;
    width:30px; height:30px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--seal);
    color:#fff;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;
    font-size:14px;
  }
  .faq-a{display:flex; gap:14px; align-items:flex-start; font-size:14.5px; color:var(--ink-soft); padding-left:0;}
  .faq-a .qa-mark{
    flex-shrink:0;
    width:30px; height:30px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--moss);
    color:#fff;
    display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
    font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;
    font-size:14px;
  }

  /* ===== 最終CTA ===== */
  .final-cta{
    position:relative;
    border-radius:40px;
    background:linear-gradient(155deg, #F6CFA0, #E89A5C 70%);
    padding:70px 50px;
    text-align:center;
    overflow:hidden;
    margin:0 28px;
    max-width:1024px;
    margin:0 auto;
  }
  .final-cta::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    top:-60px; right:-60px;
    width:220px; height:220px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
  }
  .final-cta::after{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    bottom:-80px; left:-40px;
    width:260px; height:260px;
    border-radius:50%;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  }
  .final-cta h2{
    position:relative;
    font-size:clamp(26px, 3.6vw, 36px);
    color:#fff;
    line-height:1.6;
    margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .final-cta p{
    position:relative;
    color:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
    font-size:16px;
    margin-bottom:36px;
  }
  .final-ctas{
    position:relative;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    gap:16px;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .final-cta .btn-primary{background:#fff; color:var(--seal); box-shadow:0 16px 32px -10px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);}
  .final-cta .btn-primary:hover{background:#FFF8EF;}
  .final-cta .btn-secondary{background:transparent; color:#fff; border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);}
  .final-cta .btn-secondary:hover{border-color:#fff; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);}

  /* ===== フッター ===== */
  footer{padding:64px 0 36px; color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:13.5px;}
  .footer-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap:40px;
    padding-bottom:40px;
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .footer-logo{
    display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    font-family:'Shippori Mincho',serif;
    font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:var(--seal);
    margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  footer h4{font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink); margin-bottom:16px; font-weight:700;}
  footer li{margin-bottom:10px;}
  footer a:hover{color:var(--seal);}
  .footer-bottom{padding-top:28px; text-align:center; font-size:12.5px;}

  /* ===== レスポンシブ ===== */
  @media (max-width:860px){
    nav{position:fixed; top:73px; left:0; right:0; background:var(--paper); flex-direction:column; padding:24px 28px; gap:20px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); transform:translateY(-130%); opacity:0; transition:all 0.3s ease; pointer-events:none;}
    nav.open{transform:translateY(0); opacity:1; pointer-events:auto;}
    .menu-toggle{display:block;}
    .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr; text-align:center;}
    .hero-ctas{justify-content:center;}
    .hero-art{order:-1; max-width:280px; margin:0 auto;}
    .hero h1 .underline{margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;}
    .worry-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .solution{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .solution-art{max-width:280px; margin:0 auto;}
    .strengths-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .services-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .rep{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .rep-photo{max-width:300px; margin:0 auto 30px;}
    .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:28px;}
    section{padding:64px 0;}
    .final-cta{padding:50px 26px;}
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    *{transition:none !important; animation:none !important;}
  }

  :focus-visible{
    outline:3px solid var(--apricot-deep);
    outline-offset:3px;
    border-radius:6px;
  }

  .sp-only{display:none;}
  @media (max-width:600px){
    .sp-only{display:inline;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a href="#top" class="logo">
      <span class="logo-mark">青</span>
      あおぞら司法書士事務所
    </a>
    <nav id="nav">
      <a href="#worry">お悩み</a>
      <a href="#service">サービス</a>
      <a href="#flow">相談の流れ</a>
      <a href="#rep">代表紹介</a>
      <a href="#faq">よくある質問</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">無料相談はこちら</a>
    </nav>
    <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="メニューを開く" aria-expanded="false">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="top">

  <!-- ===== ヒーロー ===== -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div>
        <span class="hero-eyebrow"><span class="dot"></span>愛知県の会社設立・不動産登記サポート</span>
        <h1>
          はじめての手続きでも、<br>
          <span class="accent">大丈夫です。</span>
          <svg class="underline" viewBox="0 0 220 16" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2 10 C 50 2, 170 2, 218 10" stroke="#F2A65A" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">
          愛知県で会社設立・不動産登記をサポートしています。<br>
          <strong>分からないままでも大丈夫。</strong>まずはお気軽にご相談ください。<br>
          ひとつひとつ、ゆっくりご一緒に進めていきましょう。
        </p>
        <div class="hero-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">無料相談はこちら</a>
          <a href="tel:0120000000" class="btn btn-secondary">📞 お電話でもご相談いただけます</a>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-note">まずはお話だけでも大丈夫です。押し売りは一切いたしません。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-art">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="あおぞら司法書士事務所 ロゴ" style="width:100%;max-width:420px;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== 共感パート ===== -->
  <section class="worry" id="worry">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="section-eyebrow">EMPATHY</span>
        <h2>こんなお悩みは<br class="sp-only">ありませんか？</h2>
        <p>はじめての方の多くが、同じような不安を抱えています。<br>あなただけではありません。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="worry-grid">
